17
00:00:38,180 --> 00:00:40,819
And we have a responsibility biblically

18
00:00:40,819 --> 00:00:44,220
to take the gospel to every creature.

19
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:47,500
We have a responsibility here in our local Jerusalem,

20
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,860
